<p><b>Eastern</b>
</p>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120321195446/http://orthodoxy.org.au/eng/index.php?p=78">Holy Anointing of the Sick</a> article from the <a href="/wiki/Moscow_Patriarchate" class="mw-redirect" title="Moscow Patriarchate">Moscow Patriarchate</a></li>
