<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20070927123949/http://stjohndc.org/Russian/what/e_Unction.htm">The Mystery of Unction</a> Russian Orthodox Cathedral of St. John the Baptist, Washington, DC</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://ukmidcopts.org/images/gallery/2006/bhm_bright_saturday/Apocalypse%20&amp;%20easter%20liturgey%20064_resize_jpg.jpg">Coptic Unction on Holy Saturday</a> (Photo)</li></ul>
